/* Regular nodes */

Node "Brahmin1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What do you mean \"odd symptoms\"?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Abnormal symptoms. Such as the shakes or trouble standing up." linkto "Brahmin1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually nevermind that. Can I ask you some other questions?" linkto "1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Brahmin1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well there were a few like that. I didn't know what to do for them so I sent them to the hospital in Salvation."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Interesting. How long ago was this?" linkto "Brahmin1a1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ok Thanks. Can I ask you about some other things now." linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How do I get to Salvation?" linkto "Brahmin1a2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. I could use some medical attention now." linkto "2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. I'll leave you to your work now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Brahmin1a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hmm.... about 3 weeks ago I think. There were 4 of them. Why are you asking?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well I'm investigating a disease carried by brahmin and fatal to anyone who eats from an infected brahmin." linkto "Brahmin1a1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Brahmin1a1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh my! And you think these patients of mine have that disease?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm not entirely sure, but I highly suspect it." linkto "Brahmin1a1a1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Brahmin1a1a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh. Well if I can help at all, please let me know."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I will, but for now could I ask you some other questions." linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I will, but for now I am in need of your services." linkto "2"  notes "this option should only be visible if the PC is injured, poisoned, or radiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I will, and thank you for offering. Now I'll leave you to your work." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Ha! I'm not sharing my glory with anyone, especially not some backwater hicktown doctor. I'm outta here." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Brahmin1a2"
notes "As of this node, Salvation should be marked on the players map if it has not already been found or marked."
{
NPCText "Okay, when you leave Crossroads.... You know, I'll just mark it on your map for you. That will be a lot easier, and you'll be sure to get there. Now just check your map and you'll see it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, but while I'm here, I could usesome medical attention." linkto "2"  notes "This option should only be visible if the pC is wounded, radiated, or poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Now I have a friend here who needs some help." linkto "4"  notes "This option should only be visible if the pC has a companion in tow who is wounded, radiated, or poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Now can I ask you some questions about yourself?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks Austin. I'm going to Salvation right now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "initial"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hello there. I'm Austin, the town doctor. I don't remember seeing you around Crossroads before. What's your name?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hello there. My name is <PC>. It's a pleasure to meet you Austin." linkto "1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh I'm glad I found you. My name is <PC> and I need some medical attention." linkto "2"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is slightly injured, slightly poisoned, or has taken a small dose of radiation."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The name's <PC>. I ... need help." linkto "3"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is heavily injured, heavily poisoned, or has taken a large dose of radiation."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm glad I found you Austin. I'm <PC> and I have a friend here who needs your help." linkto "4"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has any wounded, poisoned, or radiated party members present."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, I'm sorry to have disturbed you. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "subsequant"
notes "This should be the starting node for any subsequant conversations that Austin and the PC may have after the PC has talked to Austin once."
{
NPCText "Welcome back. How can I help you now?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need some help." linkto "2"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is injured, radiated, or poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I was just wanting to ask you some questions again." linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about how you left your vault again?" linkto "RedoHistory"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "One of my friends needs help." linkto "4"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has a companion NPC who is wounded, radiated, or poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I just stopped in to say hi. I'll leave you alone now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you had any patients in here with had odd symptoms?" linkto "Brahmin1"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has been informed of the brahmin quest by Ol' man Rich."
              }
}
Node "1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well how can I help you <PC>?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you some questions about yourself?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you had any patients come in with odd symptoms?" linkto "Brahmin1"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has been informed of the brahmin quest by Ol' man Rich."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm just looking around. I'll come back if I need your help." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh. What seems to be the trouble then?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm hurt. It's not real bad, but it needs to be treated before it gets infected." linkto "3a"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has more than 80% of his max hp."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[You show Austin your wound] That's what's wrong. It's hurting, and burning." linkto "3a"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has less than 80% of his max hp."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've taken a bit of poison." linkto "3b"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've soaked up some rads. I feel really sick." linkto "3c"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is radiated."
              }
}
Node "3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You sound horrible. What's wrong?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[You show Austin your wound] That's what's wrong. It's hurting, and burning." linkto "3a"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is injured."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm poisoned. It's making me sick." linkto "3b"  notes "this option should only be visible if the PC is poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've been radiated." linkto "3c"  notes "this option should only be visible if the PC is radiated."
              }
}
Node "3a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh I'm so sorry I didn't see that. Here. Let's go over to the table and I'll get to work on that. This will cost (xx) caps. You do have that much don't you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah sure. Just heal me." linkto "3a1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No I don't. Will you take (xx) caps?" linkto "3a2" conditions { CHECK_SKILL barter >= 60 } notes "This option should only be visible if the PC doesn't have as many caps as Austin asked for.\n(xx) should be 80% of the PC's total caps\nThis option should check the PC's barter skill to be 60%"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No I don't. Will you take (xx) caps?" linkto "3a3" conditions { CHECK_SKILL barter < 60 } notes "This option should only be visible if the PC doesn't have as many caps as Austin asked for.\n(xx) should be 80% of the PC's total caps\nThis option should check the PC's barter skill to be 60%"
              }
}
Node "3a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[Austin begins to sew up your wounds and apply healing ointments]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[wait for him to finish]" linkto "3a1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[2 hours later] There, all done. Just keep those wounds clean and dry for a few days and you'll be fine."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks Austin. Now can I ask you some questions?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I still need some help." linkto "3"  notes "this option should only be visible if the PC is poisoned or radiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks Austin. I'll come back if I need your help again." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "All right. I guess that will do."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks Austin." linkto "3a2a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Okay then. Go to the procedure room and wait for me, I'll be there in a little bit. I have to log this into my account books."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[go to table]" linkto "3a2a1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a2a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[you wait for what seems like hours and then finally, Austin comes over to you.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Finally! Let's get started." linkto "3a1"  notes "This option should only be visible if the player got to this node through barganing to have his hit points restored."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Finally! Let's get started." linkto "3b1"  notes "This option should only be visible if the player got to this node through barganing to have his poison levels removed."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Finally! Let's get started." linkto "3c1a"  notes "This option should only be visible if the player got to this node through barganing to have his radiation levels removed."
              }
}
Node "3a3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No I'm sorry. I already charge a base rate. I'll lose money if I charge any less."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But I honestly don't have enough money. [looking at Austin with big, sad eyes] Can't you please help me?" linkto "3a3a" conditions { CHECK_SKILL speech > 50, CHECK_STAT charisma > 5 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But I honestly don't have enough money. [looking at Austin with big, sad eyes] Can't you please help me?" linkto "3a3b" conditions { CHECK_SKILL speech < 51, CHECK_STAT charisma < 6 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alright. I understand. Can I ask you some questions then?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "You call yourself a doctor!? I would be ashamed of myself if i were a doctor and refused to help someone in need, simply over a few caps. I am leaving, and I may not ever return." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a3a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh all right. But don't be telling averyone about this. If everyone uses that trick on me I'll be flat broke in less than a month."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thank you so much. And don't worry, I won't tell anyone about this. I'll keep it between you and me." linkto "3a1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. I appreciate you helping me." linkto "3a1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3a3b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No, I'm sorry. I honestly can't. I would really like to help you, but I just can't afford it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine, here's the money." linkto "3a1"  notes "This option should remove the amount of caps specified by Austin."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well can I ask you something then?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn! I'll have to come back when I get more money." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh ok. Well come over to the table and I'll get an anti-venom started. This is going to cost (xx) caps. Do you have that much on you? "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's the money." linkto "3b1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No I don't. Will you take (xx) caps? That's all I have." linkto "3a2" conditions { CHECK_SKILL barter >= 60 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No I don't. Will you take (xx) caps? That's all I have." linkto "3a3" conditions { CHECK_SKILL gambling < 60 } notes ""
              }
}
Node "3b1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[Austin inserts a rather large needle into your arm and a thick, yellow liquid starts to enter your veins. Soon afterwards, you pass out.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[sleep it off]" linkto "3b1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3b1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[16 hours later, you begin to wake up]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn! ...... It feels like someone was playing the drums on my head .... with sledgehammers." linkto "3b1a1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Damn, my head is pounding. What the fuck did you do to me? I've got to get out of here." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3b1a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah.. I'm sorry about that. The band and I got a little carried away while we were practicing. [he chuckles lightly]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's funny Austin. But really, why does my head hurt so damn much?" linkto "3b1a1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Very funny smartass. I'm leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3b1a1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "It's just a temporary side effect of the anti-venom. The pain could wear off in a few hours, or it could take up to a day."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh ok. Well thanks for helping me out. Could I ask you some questions?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks for getting rid of the poison for me, but I need some more help." linkto "2"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC is injured or radiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks for the help Austin but I need to be going now. I'll come back if I get into trouble again." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
