              }
}
Node "4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Really? Well let's have a look then."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's <NPC#> over there." linkto "4a"  notes "<NPC#> represents the order in which the NPC joined the PC on his quest. For example; If Sulik was the first NPC to join the PC then the player option would actually read as \"It's Sulik over there.\"\n\nThis option needs to be automatically generated for each NPC that the PC has with him but only visible for the NPC's that need healing."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How much to get all of them healed up?" linkto "4b"  notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has more than one NPC with him who is wounded, radiated, or poisoned."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually nevermind. I'll deal with that later. Can I ask you some questions." linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually nevermind. They'll be ok. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
