}
Node "A-Q"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I suppose. I am a little busy so please make it quick."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where are you from? You seem different than most people I've met since I left home." linkto "A-Q1" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception > 6 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you lived in Crossroads your whole life?" linkto "A-Q1" conditions { CHECK_STAT strength < 7 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where did you get your medical training?" linkto "A-Q2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A-Q1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I'm actually from a vault north of here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really? So am I. What number is your vault?" linkto "A-Q1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Interesting. I've heard about those vaults. Why did you leave?" linkto "Vaultdeath3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A-Q1a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Really? That's amazing. My vault was Vault 27. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Was Vault 27? As in it no longer exists?" linkto "A-Q1a1" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception > 5 } notes "this option should only be visible if the PC has a perception of 6 or higher"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where is your Vault? I want to go there." linkto "Vaultdeath2" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception < 6 } notes "This option should only be visible if the PC has a perception of less than 6."
              }
}
Node "A-Q1a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "That's right. It was destroyed a few years ago."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How?" linkto "Vaultdeath1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A-Q2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I got my medical training back home."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And where is that?" linkto "A-Q2a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A-Q2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "A vault, about 6 weeks north from here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "A vault!? I come from a vault. Vault 31." linkto "A-Q1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "A vault? That's interesting, but I really need something else right now." linkto "A-Q2a1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Yeah right. A vault my ass! I'm outta here." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A-Q2a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh. Well then, what do you need?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need some medical attention." linkto "2"  notes "this option should only be visible if the PC is injured, poisoned, or radiated."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually nevermind. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well it happened like this...."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[listen to his story]" linkto "Vaultdeath3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "It was about a 6 week walk north of here. But it was destroyed a few years ago."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What? How was it destroyed?" linkto "Vaultdeath1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I don't know how or why, but the self destruct sequence kept activating on it's own. The techs always got it stopped, but never could figure out why it kept activating."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really? That's strange." linkto "Vaultdeath4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fascinating, but can I ask you some other questions." linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Every time that the self destruct started, we normal citizens were supposed to evacuate, but over the years, most people stopped because it always got cancelled. The last time the self destruct went off, only about 50 of us actually evacuated the vault like we were told."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What happened next?" linkto "Vaultdeath5"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "So those of us who actually did evacuate waited for the all clear signal about a mile from the vault. We waited beyond the usual time it took and started to get worried. The leader of our evacuation group, Johnathan, he called the vault on the radio to ask what the problem was."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Did he get through to anyone?" linkto "Vaultdeath6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "This is looking to be a long story. Can I ask you something else first?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Actually, I'm going to leave now. I have better things to do than listen to you tell a sob story." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath6"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah, he got through to the overseer. He said that they couldn't get the self destruct to abort and there was only a few minutes left. He said the people who had stayed were in a panic and all hell had broken loose as they tried to evacuate the vault."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh goodness. Did they make it out?" linkto "Vaultdeath7"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Vaultdeath7"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Not a one, they couldn't get far enough away. A couple of guys from my group went back to check on the vault, but when they came back, the looks on their faces said it all. Our home was destroyed, burried under 1000 tons of dirt and rock. [Austin sighs heavily]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh Austin, I'm so sorry. What did you and the other survivors do?" linkto "migrate1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait a minute, explain about the self destruct again." linkto "Vaultdeath1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "migrate1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, after the truth about the vault had sank in, we started thinking about starting a town. But we realized that we didn't have anything to form a town upon. After a lengthy, tearfull debate, we decided that the best thing to do would be split up into small groups and head in different directions."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why?" linkto "migrate2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "migrate2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well we realized the chance of any one town being able to fully support so many refugees was very slim at best. We decided that small groups of 10-20 would be best. So we devided up as best we could and started walking in different directions."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How many were in your group?" linkto "feud1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hold on, I missed part of that. Could you go over that last part again?" linkto "migrate1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "feud1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "There were fifteen of us in my group. We started out on our journey with hope and optimism, but after the first week, the mood had quickly turned to hopelessness and despair. After another week a feud broke out between two of the members. Jonathan wanted to try and settle down near a stream that we found, but Robert thought it best to keep moving."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what happened?" linkto "feud2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "feud2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well the rest of us were forced to choose sides. 5 of us chose to keep moving, but the others stayed and started a settlement. They named it New Hope."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So those that stayed, could they still be alive?" linkto "feud3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "feud3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No. A few months after I got here I heard that some explorers came across the site and found nothing but bones and a couple of collapsed sheds. It seems that they had water, but no way to grow or catch any food. The explorers reported that teeth marks found on a lot of the bones appeared to be human. It seems that they turned into cannibals."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh my... That's horrible. So what happened with the other 5 people?" linkto "starve1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did the feud start again?" linkto "feud1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "starve1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well obviously, I was one of the five that decided to keep moving. It's a good thing too.... [he shivers] So anyway, we traveled for another couple of weeks, by that time our rations were pretty much gone. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really?" linkto "starve2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "starve2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well yeah. The survival packs that we brought from the vaults weren't meant to keep us fed forever. Lucky for us, the overseer had enough foresight to make us take them whenever we evacuated, otherwise none of us would have survived more than a week."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah thank goodness for that overseer. So what happened next? I'd say you guys were getting pretty hungry." linkto "starve3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "starve3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "We sure were, but that wasn't really a problem for long."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why's that?" linkto "attack1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait, I must have missed something. Can you go over that last part again?" linkto "starve2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's enough for now. I need to get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well one day while we were traveling I noticed a group of men walking nearby. We yelled for help, assuming that they knew where a town would be. But as they came closer to us, we realized that they were odd men. They were huge, and green. They all had massive muscles and were at least 9 feet tall. Most of them seemed stupid though and just did what one of the smart ones told them to do."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Giant green men!?" linkto "attack2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah. And that's not the worst part. After they got ot us, they attacked us. I ran as fast as I could and managed to get away, but the others, I'm not sure, but I think that Richard, Adriana, and Alexia were captured and I know that Jim was killed. After a couple of days I went back to the spot where they had attacked us. I found Jim's body, but there was no trace of the others."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So they were taken then?" linkto "attack3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I can only assume. The last I saw, those giant men had all four of my friends surrounded. I don't think any of them could have gotten away. I wish I could have helped them... [tears start to roll down his cheek but he quickly gets them under control]... but there was nothing I could do for them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Did you ever look for your friends?" linkto "attack4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "For a long time I was too scared to even go back out into the wastes. By the time I worked up the nerve to search, there was no trace of them. I asked around, but aside from the odd caravan reporting an attack, there was no trace of those giant men. After a while, people stopped seeing them all together. It's like they went into hiding, or died maybe......"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hmm.... Well if I see them I'll be sure and kick the dogshit out of them for you." linkto "attack4a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well I hope I never see them. Those guys sound like monsters." linkto "attack4b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm a bit confused. Can you go over the attack again?" linkto "attack1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear that. Can I ask you something else now?" linkto "A-Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's bad. Butyou know, I need to go now. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack4a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Ha! I would appreciate that. But seriously, if you ever come across those guys, run. Run for your life and don't look back."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I could handle it, but let's drop that. How did you get to Crossroads?" linkto "home1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I can take 'em. But look, I have to go. I'll come back if I need anything." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "attack4b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "They are. If you ever see any, run. Run for your life and don't look back."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh I will. Now tell me, how did you get to Crossroads?" linkto "home1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I will, don't worry. But we've talked enough. I need to get going now. I'll stop by if I need anything." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "home1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well while I was checking out the area where we were attacked, I picked up the remaining rations that the others had dropped and started traveling again. After about four or five days I came upon Crossroads."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So then you asked to stay here, right?" linkto "home2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "home2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Wrong. When I first walked into town I noticed a man lying in the fetal position in a pool of his own vomit. He was holding his stomach and screaming in pain. I imediately knew that he had been poisoned and ran over to give him some anti-venom that I had in my vault survival kit. After a few hours he started to feel better and within a day, he was fine."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really? It's good you came when you did." linkto "home3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "home3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah, for both of us really. After the town found out I was a doctor they all asked me to stay here. I even get paid 40 caps a week. And I was just looking for a place to take me in. [he laughs] Well that's how I ended up here. I hope that satisfies your curiosity. Now I really must be getting back to work. I've spent far too much time talking about the past."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait a second. How did you get to Crossroads again?" linkto "home1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you go over some of that again?" linkto "RedoHistory"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow, thanks for telling me your story but I'll leave you alone now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "RedoHistory"
notes "Only the parts that the PC has heard should be visible."
{
NPCText "I guess. Which part?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me how the vault blew?" linkto "Vaultdeath1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me of your migration." linkto "migrate1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What started that feud again?" linkto "feud1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about your rations? When did they run out again?" linkto "starve1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about the attack on your group again." linkto "attack1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry, one more time. When did you find Crossroads?" linkto "home1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, nevermind. Let me ask you something else." linkto "1"  notes ""
              }
}
